---
import { Clock } from '@lucide/astro';
---
<!-- Daily Life / Pola Pembinaan Section -->
<section id="kehidupan" class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-24 bg-background overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="text-left md:text-center mb-10 md:mb-16 reveal">
            <span class="text-gold font-semibold text-xs md:text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block">Kehidupan Asrama</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-primary mb-4 md:mb-6">Pola Hidup & Kegiatan Santri</h2>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm md:text-base mb-6 md:mb-8">Kami mendidik santriwati dengan metode **Tarbiyah Tasyghiul Thullab** (aktif berkegiatan positif) untuk menanamkan etos ibadah dan kemandirian sejak dini.</p>
            
            <!-- Related Hadith on Akhlak -->
            <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto bg-card rounded-2xl p-5 border border-border/40 shadow-sm">
                <p class="font-arabic text-2xl text-primary leading-relaxed mb-3">إِنَّمَا بُعِثْتُ لِأُتَمِّمَ صَالِحَ الْأَخْلَاقِ</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted/90 leading-relaxed font-medium">"Sesungguhnya aku diutus hanyalah untuk menyempurnakan kebaikan akhlak." (Hadits Riwayat Ahmad, no. 8952 & Al-Bukhari dalam Al-Adab Al-Mufrad, no. 273)</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Layout Split Grid -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center reveal">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl text-primary mb-6">Agenda Harian Santriwati</h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <Clock class="w-5 h-5" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">02.30 - Subuh</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted">Qiyamul Lail berjamaah, diikuti wirid aurad khas (Wirdul Lathif, Sholatul Fatih, Rotibul Haddad).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <Clock class="w-5 h-5" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Setelah Subuh & Dzuhur</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted">Kuliah Tujuh Menit (Kultum) santriwati bergilir, dilanjutkan muhadatsah aktif Bahasa Arab siang hari.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <Clock class="w-5 h-5" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Sore Hari (Setelah Ashar)</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted">Praktik mengabdikan ilmu dengan mengajar langsung di Taman Pendidikan Al-Qur'an (TPQ) sekitar pondok.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <Clock class="w-5 h-5" />
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Kamis - Sabtu</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted">Tadribur Muhadloroh (latihan pidato) dan dakwah lapangan/sosial berkala di masyarakat.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-premium aspect-[4/3] border border-border/50 bg-white p-2">
                <img src="/images/boarding-activities.jpg" alt="Kegiatan Santriwati" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
